	    <p>
	      The total variance is <m>V_x+V_y = 3/2+1=5/2</m>.
	    </p>
	  </li>
	  <li>
	    <p>
	      The variance is greatest in the direction
	      <m>\uvec=\twovec{0.79}{0.62}</m> where
	      <m>V_{\uvec}=2.28</m>.
	    </p>
	  </li>
	</ol>
      </p>
    </solution>
